## 📦 Adding Features

### Add a new route

```typescript
const myPlugin = createPlugin('my-feature', async (fastify) => {
  fastify.get('/my-route', async () => ({
    message: 'Hello from my route!'
  }));
});

await app.register(myPlugin);
```

### Add middleware

```typescript
const middlewarePlugin = createPlugin('my-middleware', async (fastify) => {
  fastify.addHook('preHandler', async (request, reply) => {
    console.log(`${request.method} ${request.url}`);
  });
});

await app.register(middlewarePlugin);
```

## 🚀 Deployment

### Build for production

```bash
npm run build
npm start
```

### Docker (optional)

```dockerfile
FROM node:22-alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci --only=production
COPY dist ./dist
EXPOSE 3000
CMD ["npm", "start"]
```

